      "__id__": 57
    },
    "_enabled": true,
    "__prefab": null,
    "eventType": 2,
    "prompt": "The misery of the region is unbearable. <br />\nMuch of the towns are now full with dust, bones, and ashes. <br />\nA couple years ago, something called<color=#FFFF00> La corrupción </color><br/>This curse spread like a plague.\nBut this plague didn't just killed people, it removed all the humanity of the body, and the remaining flesh and bones transformed into something else. Some people got insane, but others were transformed into something that can not be described as something native to this world. <br />",
    "options": [
      "Continue"
    ],
    "optionSelected": 0,
    "eventImage": {
      "__uuid__": "9bede9cd-4fb4-4b5a-8299-33ff6f6105b2@f9941",
